==German==
===Etymology===
From {{OHG.}} ''[[ostan]]'', related to the Indo-European root ''*ausos'' "dawn", compare {{L.}} ''[[aurora]]'', and {{L.}} ''[[auster]]'', which, probably due to a re-orientation, means "South".

===Noun===
'''Osten''' ''m''
# [[East]]
